announcements.name: [March 19] Community Center Upgrade
announcements.description:
Hello!
A new city project has released for an upgrade to the community center. Maybe Clerk Seraphine can afford more ballot papers now. The mayors seem to be busy and preparing something great - perhaps new mayor perks are in store?
